title: ME! (feat. Brendon Urie of Panic! At The Disco)
description:
ME! was the debut song that brought us into the Lover era! The video is filled with pretty colors, lots of Easter eggs, and a surprise announcement that Taylor was waiting to make! Nick, Amy, Ana and Lacey break down this song and discuss that controversial lyric.
What did we miss? What would you like to hear next? Let us know!
